edBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T08:10:18.000Z","msg":"貴&amp;食唔飽<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"889fd04e291fc3e5e1da24c2e4a00533228f6ad7","tid":2391372,"uid":110832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T08:18:03.000Z","msg":"名"},{"pid":"ca907de21d404e03f0ea5d07dd13e2381b5d15d4","tid":2391372,"uid":13361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"889fd04e291fc3e5e1da24c2e4a00533228f6ad7","tid":2391372,"uid":110832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T08:18:03.000Z","msg":"名"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T08:19:04.000Z","msg":"第一張圖塊木板有刻名的<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"533daa94a04f0a32be179f5d5fa2983b86e3b8af","tid":2391372,"uid":1254,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"261a969d86707a3cae6e8a31930b96e15174aaa0","tid":2391372,"uid":13361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T07:30:10.000Z","msg":"以前剩係開晚市的，但無得晚市堂食後，可以book位食午市 限時90分鐘 人少少幾chill <br />\n老闆會錄音覆wtsapp<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好有禮貌同耐性<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n入店之前店員會幫你全身噴一噴消一消毒 入到去枱面仲有搓手液 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />去咁多黃店都未試過咁衛生<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EGmNGXq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEGmNGXq.jpg&h=b78f8b01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黑糖裸麥包配cream cheese $20<br />\n以前是好似outback咁任食的<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但因為疫情影響 生意唔好 就比錢先有得吃 第一啖就咁食個包甜咗啲 但之後搽咗cream cheese就好食到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n食物逐樣上比你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔會擺到成枱都係食唔切攤到凍晒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢樣中價西餐黎講加好多分<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3fYkhzX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3fYkhzX.jpg&h=df464469&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n粉紅岩鹽安格斯T骨牛扒 $468 （14-16安士）<br />\n杜汶澤食個陣仲係賣緊$398<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />小妹食貴咗$70<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n牛扒又大塊又好味<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有咬口又有牛味<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />鍾意食淋啲嘅牛可以叫和牛肉眼扒$438 一樣係14-16安士<br />\n<br />\n雖然配菜好似好簡單咁 但係車厘茄上面啲醋係有濃濃嘅果香<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好撚fresh<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />中和返成口炸蒜片嘅臭味<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ory8ruQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fory8ruQ.png&h=d28c7f8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一飛沖天雞$198<br />\n熱到仆街 但比兩隻膠手套你食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />根本熱到拆唔到隻雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />小妹唯有接住佢不斷滴緊嘅雞汁試吓味先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好好味呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />即刻忍住180度嘅高溫都要抆隻雞髀黎食下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嫩滑juicy又入味<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過都係唔建議大家食 小妹食到隻手生水泡<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽講廚師發辨又貴又伏 所以老細已經取消咗 依家堂食得返單點<br />\n<br />\n小妹下次會試吓佢啲幾抵屌嘅外賣餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw 老細得幾枱客可唔可以分開啲坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />明明周圍大把位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n連豬指數 ： 10/10 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T08:22:03.000Z","msg":"我發現你專係去埋啲戇鳩店比人搵笨"},{"pid":"d8c1fd574c8115cad9e98cdf07e7535ea57d9f54","tid":2391372,"uid":13361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"533daa94a04f0a32be179f5d5fa2983b86e3b8af","tid":2391372,"uid":1254,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"261a969d86707a3cae6e8a31930b96e15174aaa0","tid":2391372,"uid":13361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"rep