lass=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n食物逐樣上比你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔會擺到成枱都係食唔切攤到凍晒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢樣中價西餐黎講加好多分<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3fYkhzX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3fYkhzX.jpg&h=df464469&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n粉紅岩鹽安格斯T骨牛扒 $468 （14-16安士）<br />\n杜汶澤食個陣仲係賣緊$398<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />小妹食貴咗$70<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n牛扒又大塊又好味<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有咬口又有牛味<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />鍾意食淋啲嘅牛可以叫和牛肉眼扒$438 一樣係14-16安士<br />\n<br />\n雖然配菜好似好簡單咁 但係車厘茄上面啲醋係有濃濃嘅果香<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好撚fresh<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />中和返成口炸蒜片嘅臭味<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ory8ruQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fory8ruQ.png&h=d28c7f8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一飛沖天雞$198<br />\n熱到仆街 但比兩隻膠手套你食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />根本熱到拆唔到隻雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />小妹唯有接住佢不斷滴緊嘅雞汁試吓味先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好好味呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />即刻忍住180度嘅高溫都要抆隻雞髀黎食下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嫩滑juicy又入味<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過都係唔建議大家食 小妹食到隻手生水泡<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽講廚師發辨又貴又伏 所以老細已經取消咗 依家堂食得返單點<br />\n<br />\n小妹下次會試吓佢啲幾抵屌嘅外賣餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw 老細得幾枱客可唔可以分開啲坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />明明周圍大把位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n連豬指數 ： 10/10 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T08:22:03.000Z","msg":"我發現你專係去埋啲戇鳩店比人搵笨"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T08:28:32.000Z","msg":"窮閪食唔起幾百蚊一餐就話人呃錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T08:30:06.000Z","msg":"我無咁講過喎<br />\n原來你覺得幾百蚊一餐係好貴呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb8e08f80d958c63b35e112cfc74806d3c09b525","tid":2391372,"uid":47041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5228f0622f376a5124032835e9a949874b49b1db","tid":2391372,"uid":1254,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3c2e0164556e52625988c95a2710f5bf7c99288d","tid":2391372,"uid":165336,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"533daa94a04f0a32be179f5d5fa2983b86e3b8af","tid":2391372,"uid":1254,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T08:22:03.000Z","msg":"我發現你專係去埋啲戇鳩店比人搵笨"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T08:28:32.000Z","msg":"窮閪食唔起幾百蚊一餐就話人呃錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T08:30:06.000Z","msg":"我無咁講過喎<br />\n原來你覺得幾百蚊一餐係好貴呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T08:55:44.000Z","msg":"好肉酸<br />\n食餐飯又比人搵笨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"833c8fcab15d5655245361814f0f84ad8c65ff66","tid":2391372,"uid":13361,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fb8e08f80d958c63b35e112cfc74806d3c09b525","tid":2391372,"uid":47041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5228f0622f376a5124032835e9a949874b49b1db","tid":2391372,"uid":1254,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3c2e0164556e52625988c95a2710f5bf7c99288d","tid":2391372,"uid":165336,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T08:28:32.000Z","msg":"窮閪食唔起幾百蚊一餐就話人呃錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T08:30:06.000Z","msg":"我無咁講過喎<br />\n原來你覺得幾百蚊一餐係好貴呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T08:55:44.000Z","msg":"好肉酸<br />\n食餐飯又比人搵笨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T09:15:10.000Z","msg":"<img src